<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>致我的女王殿下</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ma+Shan+Zheng&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@300;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --princess-pink: #fce4ec;
            --royal-gold: #d4af37;
            --magic-white: #ffffff;
            --fairytale-rose: #ff85a1;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--princess-pink);
            /* 添加梦幻渐变和星光感背景 */
            background-image: radial-gradient(#fff 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            color: #5d4037;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
        }

        /* 顶部华丽装饰 */
        header {
            height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: var(--dark-pink);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px #fff, 4px 4px 0px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tiara {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px gold);
        }

        /* 欧式壁画相框设计 */
        .mural-container {
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .mural-frame {
            position: relative;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 12px solid #fff;
            /* 金色雕花边框效果 */
            outline: 2px solid var(--royal-gold);
            outline-offset: -8px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 0 0 4px #fff,
                0 0 0 6px var(--royal-gold),
                0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            max-width: 90%;
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        .mural-frame::before {
            content: "✿";
            position: absolute;
            top: -25px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: var(--princess-pink);
            color: var(--royal-gold);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        .mural-frame img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            /* 让图片带有一点油画质感 */
            filter: sepia(10%) contrast(1.1);
        }

        .mural-caption {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-family: 'Ma Shan Zheng', cursive;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--royal-gold);
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* 童话文字区域 */
        .story-text {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            margin: 30px 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 50% / 10% 10% 10% 10%; /* 弧形边缘 */
            border: 1px solid var(--royal-gold);
            line-height: 2;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--royal-gold);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        /* 魔法星光闪烁动画 */
        @keyframes sparkle {
            0% { opacity: 0.3; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
            100% { opacity: 0.3; }
        }

        .magic-dot {
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: gold;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: sparkle 2s infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="tiara">👑</div>
        <h1>女王殿下</h1>
        <p>在这个童话的世界里，你永远是主角</p>
    </header>

    <div class="mural-container">
        <div class="mural-frame">
            <img src="mom-01.jpg" alt="妈妈的照片">
            <div class="mural-caption">永恒的优雅</div>
        </div>

        <section class="story-text">
            在很久很久以前，<br>
            有一位温柔的仙女来到了我的身边。<br>
            她没有魔法棒，却用双手织出了最温暖的家。<br>
            亲爱的妈妈，节日快乐。
        </section>

        <div class="mural-frame">
            <img src="mom-02.jpg" alt="妈妈的照片">
            <div class="mural-caption">时光里的温柔</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>✦ 公主殿下的私人画廊 ✦</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
